== Bimwe mu bice byo mu gihugu cy u Rwanda byagarage ikibazo k' ituritswa ry'intambi ==
Abaturage ba Jabana bo mu mugi wa kigali bagaragaje kubangamirwa ni ituritswa ry'intambi mu gihe hakorwaga umuhanda , mu murenge wa rusenge mu karere ka nyarugure <ref>https://rba.co.rw/post/Bamwe-mu-batuye-muri-Nyaruguru-babangamiwe-no-guturitsa-intambi</ref>,mu karere ka Karongi na Rubavu  naho hagararagara ikibazo k' iuritswa ry intambi ndetse ni ingaruka iturika rigira kubaturage <ref>Abangirijwe n’intambi mu gukora umuhanda Karongi-Rubavu bijejwe ingurane - Kigali Today</ref>.

